<div class="box"><strong>Status:</strong> READY FOR MVP SIGN-OFF (within SL-028 scope)</div>

<h2>How It Works</h2>
<ul>
<li>Receipt upload creates draft expense and starts OCR processing.</li>
<li>OCR provider selection supports Azure DI / vision path / safe stub fallback.</li>
<li>Extracted fields hydrate expense draft (vendor, date, amount, tax, category, line items).</li>
<li>Confidence and risk metadata are produced for review.</li>
<li>Async queue integration and workflow handoff are present.</li>
</ul>

